What you need to know:

Other projects that President Kenyatta has promised to complete include Nyamaiya stadium in Nyamaiya ward of West Mugirango constituency, which will be constructed to a standard stadia and Ekerenyo sub county hospital in Nyamira North, which will be advanced to a level five facility to improve it from its sub-county status, at Sh100 million.The county headquarters whose construction started in 2018 will also be completed at an approximated cost of Sh200 million.